data.description: This updated 3b 2b house features a large open living area with wood burning stove,  a huge laundry room and private office gym on a very quiet 2.02 acres is a must see. This property has big oak trees, a creek, big back concrete patio, and located in a secluded area of the neighborhood. The home was newly (about a year) remodeled with all new flooring, paint, cabinets, windows and an open concept that brings a warm and welcoming feel. You are literally minutes from anything you need, yet able to enjoy country living at it's best. A large shop with electric and a multi-car carport are some of the other amenities found with this property. Stainless steel kitchen appliances and granite are also present. This property will not last long - come take a look!  PROPERTY CAN ALSO BE PURCHASED FULLY FURNISHED AT A NEGOTIATED PRICE!!!
